===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  connection_aborted(): int~

Checks whether the client disconnected.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

This function has no parameters.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

Returns 1 if client disconnected, 0 otherwise.

